yellow box follows behind and is now being cut at the same time. Each taking 10

16
00:01:00,308 --> 00:01:05,285
seconds. In the next 10 seconds, the red box is taped, the yellow box is folded,

17
00:01:05,285 --> 00:01:09,520
and the blue box is cut, that's 30 seconds. After this point you can see another

18
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:11,920
box will come off the assembly line every 10 seconds.
